<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mithiengte chiehna a lamlui pha hawh in,
 Lalpen in I mau A pui zel;
 Vana I In uh zuonin I chieh ui,
 Sun aksi I chungah avak.

[V2]
 Van In nuom zuonin I chieh ui,
 Kipahna, hinna lukhuk khu din;
 I tun tieng kipak mah mah hitiu,
 Bittak in gam nuomah.

[V3]
 2. Tatsate bangin lam lui pha hawh in,
 Tuhin Zion zuona chieh in;
 Lalpen thupiek in In zuonin I chieh,
 I thaumei guotsa leh vaksa'n.

[V4]
 3. Ginna detin, lam lui pha chuh hawh in,
 Kihehpih a kilungguol in;
 Kipak hitiu Lalpen mu ding I hiu,
 Amah tawh kivawp zing tai tiu.

[V5]
 4. Jordan tuikinawk luipang vawt lakah,
 I kenga dingin um mahleng;
 Lalpen in agal ei kaihpih intin,
 Kumsawt in A pakla sai tiu.</lyrics>
<title>SAFE IN THE GLORY LAND</title>
<hymn_number>391</hymn_number>
</song>